3/26, Ke Huy Quan is overcome with emotion as he accepts Oscar<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://tw.voicetube.com/videos/176090">https://tw.voicetube.com/videos/176090</a><!-- m --><br /><br />1.Ke Huy Quan is the Oscar winner of the actor in a supportive role in the movie of “Everything Everywhere All at Once”. How do you feel when you know that he won the Oscar? And the speech he delivered so emotionally?<br />2.It took him almost 30 years to make a comeback to the movie industry. Can you describe your feelings for him in one word?<br />3.According to your feelings for him, do you have the same or similar experiences in your life? Can you share with us? (It doesn’t have to be as big as winning the Oscar, small goals or tasks will do.)<br />4.If you have a chance to go upon to a stage to deliver a Thank-you speech to someone who has played an important role in pursuit of your goals or dreams? What would like to say? <br /><br />Agenda:<br />7:00-7:05 pm Opening Remarks<br />Session 1:<br />7:05-7:40 pm <br />Individual Presentation<br />7:40-8:00<br />Group  discussion.<br />Session 2.<br />8:00-8:40 pm<br />Individual <br />8：40-9:00 pm<br />Group  discussion.<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://zoomtw.zoom.us/j/92987266213?pw">https://zoomtw.zoom.us/j/92987266213?pw</a><!-- m --> ...<br />Meeting ID:929 8726 6213<br />Password:112233<br /><br />Taiwan to import 60 million eggs in April, May<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.taiwannews.com.tw/en/news/4843330">https://www.taiwannews.com.tw/en/news/4843330</a><!-- m --><br /><br />1.Does this shortage of eggs influence your life? <br />2.Do you know what are the main causes of this incident happened? <br />3.If you are someone who cannot live without eggs, what is your backup plan when you cannot buy eggs anymore?<br />4.Are eggs good for our health? They are studies show the benefits of the eggs while the others say otherwise. Is it because the way to cook? Or, how many eggs to eat daily?......What do you think?<br />5.Would you like to give it a try for the imported eggs?<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=48">dora</a> — Fri Mar 24, 2023 1:55 pm</p><hr />
