3/5(Sun.)Man accidentally buys two identical lottery tickets, wins two jackpots/Daily walk prevents one in 10 early deaths - study(Host: Danny)<br /><br />Agenda:<br />7:00-7:10 pm Opening Remarks<br />7:10-7:40 pm Session 1: Group Discussion<br />7:40-8:00 pm Individual Presentation<br />8:00-8:05 pm Break<br />8:05-8:40 pm Session 2: Group Discussion<br />8:40-9:00 pm Individual Presentation<br /><br />We will hold a zoom meeting only.<br /><br />Zoom meeting: Please click the link below<br /><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://zoomtw.zoom.us/j/92987266213?pw">https://zoomtw.zoom.us/j/92987266213?pw</a><!-- m --> ...<br />Meeting ID:929 8726 6213<br />Password:112233<br />--------------------------------------------<br /><br />Session 1: Man accidentally buys two identical lottery tickets, wins two jackpots<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.upi.com/Odd_News/2023/02/27/lotto-Michigan-Lottery-Fantasy-5-identical-tickets-mistake/5921677527587/">https://www.upi.com/Odd_News/2023/02/27 ... 677527587/</a><!-- m --><br />1.What do you think are the odds of winning the lottery, and how does this man's story change your perception of those odds?<br />2.If you won a large sum of money, what would you do with it? Do you agree with this man's decision to put some of it towards his son's education and save the rest?<br />3.Have you ever won a prize or lottery before? If so, what did you do with the winnings?<br />4.Do you think it was a coincidence that the man won two jackpots with the same set of numbers, or do you believe there is a strategy to increasing your chances of winning the lottery?<br />5.Some people believe that winning the lottery brings more problems than benefits. Do you agree or disagree with this sentiment, and why?<br /><br />Session 2: Daily walk prevents one in 10 early deaths - study<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.bbc.com/news/health-64790527">https://www.bbc.com/news/health-64790527</a><!-- m --><br />1.How do you currently incorporate physical activity into your daily routine?<br />2.What are some barriers that prevent you from meeting the recommended amount of weekly physical activity?<br />3.What types of physical activities do you enjoy doing, and how do they benefit your overall health?<br />4.How can workplaces and communities encourage more physical activity among their members?<br />5.How do you prioritize physical activity in your busy schedule and make time for it?<br /><br />P.S.<br />1.參加三次後，只要繳交1,000元(學生500元)，即可成為ROYAL終身會員!<br />2.請帶著開放與熱情來參加自由的全英文會話聚會~<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=12531">Danny Lin</a> — Wed Mar 01, 2023 11:46 pm</p><hr />
